PrecisAuthorization for the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to grant a 25-year ground lease to CARLINGTON AQUATIC PARK INC., together with a ten-year renewal option, with respect to some 14 hectares of land in the City of Nepean, being the site of the Watts Creek Sewage Treatment Plant, for the purpose of developing an aquatic amusement centre.
